TERMS AND CONDITIONS FOR AutoRental.com

Welcome to AutoRental, the online rental car service in Bulgaria. Please read these terms and conditions carefully before using our website or any of our services. By using our website or services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.

General Terms
a. AutoRental provides an online rental car booking service in Bulgaria.
b. Our services are available only to individuals who possess a valid driver's license and are at least 21 years old.
c. Our rental cars are subject to availability.
d. AutoRental reserves the right to refuse service to anyone without notice or explanation.
e. AutoRental may change or update these terms and conditions at any time without notice.

Reservations
a. Reservations are made online and require a valid credit card.
b. All rental car rates are quoted in Bulgarian lev and are subject to applicable taxes and fees.
c. Reservations are subject to availability and must be made at least 24 hours in advance.
d. AutoRental reserves the right to cancel any reservation at any time without notice.

Rental Cars
a. Rental cars are provided with a full tank of gas and must be returned with a full tank of gas.
b. Rental cars are rented on a daily basis and must be returned by the agreed-upon date and time.
c. Additional charges will be applied for late returns or for returning a rental car with less gas than it was rented with.
d. The renter is responsible for any damage to the rental car, regardless of fault.

Fees and Payment
a. Rental car rates are subject to applicable taxes and fees.
b. All payments must be made with a valid credit card.
c. AutoRental reserves the right to charge additional fees for any services or products requested by the renter.

Liability
a. AutoRental is not liable for any injury, loss, or damage caused by the rental car or the use of the rental car.
b. The renter is responsible for all damages and costs resulting from any accident or incident involving the rental car.
c. AutoRental is not responsible for any loss or damage to personal property left in the rental car.

Insurance
a. Rental cars are provided with basic liability insurance.
b. The renter may purchase additional insurance coverage at their own expense.

Termination
a. AutoRental reserves the right to terminate any rental car agreement at any time without notice.
b. The renter may terminate the rental car agreement at any time by returning the rental car to AutoRental.

Governing Law
a. These terms and conditions shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Bulgaria.
b. Any dispute arising out of or relating to these terms and conditions shall be resolved in the courts of Bulgaria.

Contact Information
a. For any questions or concerns about these terms and conditions or our services, please contact us at support@autorental.bg.

By using our website or services, you acknowledge that you have read and agree to these terms and conditions in compliance with the laws of Bulgaria.